    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait sorry \"goblin inventory trackers\"? i think you might have had a typo there or something lol. anyway, regarding the cycle counts, how often should we be doing those to catch the loss before it gets too high? and what kind of tech should we be using to track it better?",
